title: DEWA organises induction session for 2nd Carbon Ambassadors Programme 2015-2016 (Dubai Electricity and Water Authority) ...
text: ( Source : Dubai Electricity and Water Authority ) Tue, 20 Oct 2015 Dubai Electricity and Water Authority (DEWA) has organised an induction session for the 2nd Carbon Ambassadors Programme ( CAP ) 2015-2016, today at the InterContinental hotel
